<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Low Wallet Balance Alert</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .alert {
            background-color: #fff8e1;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        .wallet-info {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 10px;
            border-top: 1px solid #eee;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Low Wallet Balance Alert</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="alert">
        <strong>Warning:</strong> A wallet balance has fallen below the configured threshold.
    </div>
    
    <div class="wallet-info">
        <h2>Wallet Details</h2>
        <p><strong>Wallet ID:</strong> {{walletId}}</p>
        <p><strong>Wallet Address:</strong> {{walletAddress}}</p>
        <p><strong>Current Balance:</strong> {{currentBalance}} ETH</p>
        <p><strong>Threshold:</strong> {{threshold}} ETH</p>
        <p><strong>Alert Time:</strong> {{timestamp}}</p>
    </div>
    
    <p>Please ensure that this wallet has sufficient funds to continue operations. Consider topping up the wallet soon to prevent transaction failures.</p>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>This is an automated message from the Vana Relay Service monitoring system.</p>
        <p>Timestamp: {{timestamp}}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 